# PMTiles Base URL
# The manifest (year → hashed filename) is embedded at build time via @world-history-map/tiles.
# This variable controls only where the PMTiles binary files are fetched from.
#
# Development: Leave empty — vite dev middleware serves packages/tiles/dist/ at /pmtiles/
# Preview:     Set to the preview Worker URL (world-history-map-tiles-dev environment)
# Production:  Set to the production Worker URL (world-history-map-tiles-prod environment)
VITE_TILES_BASE_URL=
# Example: https://world-history-map-tiles-production.akihiro-021109.workers.dev
